<TEXT>
<P>
GENEVA, November 24 (Xinhua) -- The World Health Organization
(WHO) and United Nations Children's Fund (UNICEF) launched here
today an appeal for 35 million U.S. dollars to fight poliomyelitis
in the war-affected countries in Asia and Africa.
</P>
<P>
