"Establishing a true presence in China, one of the largest cotton
producers and consumers in the world, represents a key expansion
move for our 24-year-old international division."
</P>
<P>
Cotton Inc has been providing technical and information
services to China since 1994.
</P>
<P>
The company's Shanghai office is expected to be conducive for
the company's better understanding of the dynamics of China's
markets and its effects on global textiles.  
