construction. (Israel-Netanyahu-Settlement Promise)
</P>
<P>
- - - -
</P>
<P>
MOSCOW -- Economic recession has stopped for the first time
over the period of reforms in Russia this year, Russian Prime
Minister Viktor Chernomyrdin said here Sunday. (Russia-Economy)
</P>
