<HEADLINE> American Leach and Stark Claim ATP Doubles Title </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, November 23 (Xinhua) -- Fourth-seeds Americans Rick
Leach and Jonathan Stark ousted the Indian pair Mahesh Bhupathi
and Leander Paes 6-3, 6-4, 7-6 (7-3) to capture the ATP Tour World
