<HEADLINE> Results of Gymnastics World Cup </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BONN, November 23 (Xinhua) -- Following are the results of the
first round of the World Cup Gymnastics Tournament in Stuttgart,
Germany on Sunday:
</P>
<P>
Men's:
</P>
<P>
Vault
</P>
<P>
1. Alexei Nemov, Russia, 9.600 points
